========================================================================
README for Multi-resource Isolation Package

April 2018

========================================================================
This software package provides occupancy detection and quota adjustment for reso-urces such as cpu, memory, llc cache, memory bandwidth, and network bandwidth f-or a specific cgroup.

It is based on another open source project called Intel-cmt-cat, which provides basic support for
Intel(R) Resource Director Technology (Intel(R) RDT) including:
Cache Monitoring Technology (CMT), Memory Bandwidth Monitoring (MBM),
Cache Allocation Technology (CAT), Code and Data Prioritization (CDP)
and Memory Bandwidth Allocation (MBA).
